I"G<p>Set them in Tools -&gt; Options -&gt; Environment -&gt; Keyboard.</p>

<ul>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">File.Close</code>: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Ctrl+Shift+W</code></li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Window.MovetoPreviousTabGroup</code>: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Ctrl+Shift+Alt+[</code></li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Window.MovetoNextTabGroup</code>: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Ctrl+Shift+Alt+]</code></li>
</ul>
